headline: Kesha on ‘Nebraska,’ ‘Space’ and Stuff in Between
abstract: The pop singer and songwriter shared what she watched, wore, listened to and read over 48 hours.
lead_paragraph: “For me, music is mind-altering,” said the 32-year-old pop hell-raiser Kesha. “It can force me into a better mood, or it can force me into a more introspective mood when I don’t want to go there.”
